FRIDAY’S PUZZLE — Now this is what a Friday puzzle should be. Gettable yet challenging. Nice and open, with lots of fun, long entries. Great answers — a total of 12 unique ones, and all of them legit phrases or words.

Nicely done, Derek Bowman. You had me at EASY THERE/TIGER, SQUARE PEG, and PUPPY LOVE, but I stayed through the ENDLESS STRUGGLE and SCARY SPICE to enjoy UNDER/THE BRIDGE and SCREAM OUT.

